fields.message: This is an important private message

fields.body_text: I can, write a reply. It's my reply

There was a quick pit stop to focus on the mobile design, as it needed quite a bit of help. Development of that however is nearly complete. Because of this, a redesign of the entire homepage will also be necessary...is this an infinite loop? Unlikely! Lots of copy pasting shall help us get through this.
Another pit-stop to test some mobile features, as many things have only been checked on desktop.
Basically everything important on this list is done...we are coming to the end of the development process! From here we can move on to the next stage.

fields.title: Upcoming Features and Development Process
fields.body_text:
Since this is still in development, many of the planned features are not yet added. So, here is a list of everything that is planned, as well as more specific details that need to be added.

[b]Main Features[/b]
[list][*][s]Inventory/item system[/s][*][s]Shop/Pokemart[/s][*][s]Evolution [s]by level[/s], [s]by item[/s], and by trade[/s][*][s]Site notifications e.g. ready to hatch[/s][*][s]Park[/s][*][s]Daycare[/s], daycare eggs[*][s]EXP Share[/s][*][s]Global trade system[/s][*][s]Private messages[/s][/list]
[b]Pages[/b]

[list][*][s]Today's Interactions[/s][*][s]BBCode help page[/s][/list]
[b]Small Things[/b]

[list][*]Better EXP handling on profile pages[*]Lab reload time[*]Switch from [code]time_threshold[/code] to data table reset[*]Change position in box[*]SQLite3 to MySQL[*][s]CEDAR always online[/s][*][s]Change 'Page' to 'pg'[/s][*][s]Alter footer[/s][*]Add pagination to Pokedex[*]Party positions[/list]
[b]Flavor Text[/b]

[list][*][s]Pokemart[/s][*]Receiving Bag[*]Inventory Page, Link to receive bag[/list]
[b]Art Needed[/b]
[list][*]PC[*]Daycare Assistant[*]Receiving Pokedex[*]Receiving bag[*]Receiving park pass[/list]
[b]Temporary Handicaps[/b]

[list][*][s]Price of Poke Radar[/s][*][s]PD amount from interactions[/s][*][s]EXP from interactions[/s][*]Poke Radar steps[*][s]Time between interactions[/s][*][s]Stats from berries[/s][*][s]Total daily interaction quota[/s][*][s]Key item prices[/s][/list]
